    "description": "Survival In The Backrooms 是一款气氛恐怖的游戏，您将在超现实的走廊和房间中徘徊很长时间以寻找出口。让自己沉浸在这个神秘的世界中，尽量不要成为其居民的猎物。该游戏基于著名的creepypasta，并具有大量参考和可识别元素。探索看似无穷无尽的阈限空间寻找补给品并避开危险实体。请记住，没有办法离开 Backrooms。还没有人能够离开这里。您将不得不探索每个房间以找到有用的物品或线索，让您继续前进。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >地点</h2>你会发现自己在零级无尽的黄色房间里，在“Poolrooms”的深水池里游泳，在 150 级的绿色办公室里走来走去。通常，这些级别是一个相当大的迷宫。您应该非常小心地猜测如何离开这里，并注意不要打扰当地居民。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/46afbafc5e0c3a5a34c91097864a0676.poster.avif?t=1739796484\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/46afbafc5e0c3a5a34c91097864a0676.webm?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/46afbafc5e0c3a5a34c91097864a0676.mp4?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精华</h2>在众多不起眼的房间中，你可以突然听到奇怪的声音，破旧的电视机发出的单调嘶嘶声，然后是某人大脚的响亮的跺脚声。如果你发现自己处于这种情况，你很可能会死。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/a2b05bdd5172b72a1096ec184c5f1d9a.poster.avif?t=1739796484\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/a2b05bdd5172b72a1096ec184c5f1d9a.webm?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/a2b05bdd5172b72a1096ec184c5f1d9a.mp4?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器和物品</h2>为了在 Backrooms 中生存，您需要寻找武器和必需品并妥善处理它们。一把手枪和几颗子弹可以帮助你在与实体的相遇中幸存下来，而食物、水和药物将恢复你的力量。当然，这里的资源永远是供不应求的。把你能找到的所有东西都放在你的背包里！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/e865f3066f2e2c5bb68203bdd7ecb45a.poster.avif?t=1739796484\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/e865f3066f2e2c5bb68203bdd7ecb45a.webm?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/e865f3066f2e2c5bb68203bdd7ecb45a.mp4?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 你必须探索三个复杂的大关卡<br></li><li> 实体可以在最不可预测的地方相遇<br></li><li> 寻找武器和其他有用的物品。它将帮助您生存<br></li><li> 详细的设置菜单，管理和保存进度<br></li><li> 可识别的 Liminal Spaces 氛围</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/3ee2499adc81e47d087ea2396215046c.poster.avif?t=1739796484\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/3ee2499adc81e47d087ea2396215046c.webm?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2184110/extras/3ee2499adc81e47d087ea2396215046c.mp4?t=1739796484\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
